Package org.wmn4j.notation.elements

Class TimeSignature

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wmn4j.notation.elements.TimeSignature
  • public final class TimeSignature
extends Object
    Class for time signatures. Time signatures consist of the number of beats and the duration of each beat. For example, for the time signature 4/4 the number of beats is 4 and the duration of beat is Durations.QUARTER.
